------------------------------------------------------------------------

You can activate the driver on /dev/cuad0 by adding the following
lines to %%PREFIX%%/etc/reader.conf.d/reader.conf:

FRIENDLYNAME     "Reflex 62"
DEVICENAME       /dev/cuad0
LIBPATH          %%PREFIX%%/lib/pcsc/drivers/libslb_rf60.so
CHANNELID        0x0103F8

------------------------------------------------------------------------
